  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, okay, how about this?",
      "zh": "好，好，那這個怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "はい、はい、これでどう？",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ugh.",
      "zh": "唉。",
      "ja": "うっ。",
      "time": "00:00:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Excuse me. Where do I sign it?",
      "zh": "不好意思，我在哪裡簽名？",
      "ja": "すみません。どこにサインすればいいですか？",
      "time": "00:00:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I see you have a sword. I have one too.",
      "zh": "我看到你有把劍，我也有一把。",
      "ja": "剣を持っているね。私も持ってるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They're very madly.",
      "zh": "它們非常瘋狂。",
      "ja": "とても激しいよ。",
      "time": "00:00:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm working on it.",
      "zh": "我正在努力。",
      "ja": "今頑張ってるところだ。",
      "time": "00:00:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who am I fooling?",
      "zh": "我在騙誰呢？",
      "ja": "誰を騙してるんだ？",
      "time": "00:00:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's going to take a miracle to get me into the army.",
      "zh": "要我進軍隊得靠奇蹟了。",
      "ja": "軍隊に入るには奇跡が必要だ。",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I hear someone asked for a miracle.",
      "zh": "我聽說有人在求奇蹟。",
      "ja": "誰かが奇跡を求めていると聞いた。",
      "time": "00:00:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let me hear you say, ah!",
      "zh": "讓我聽你說，啊！",
      "ja": "さあ、あーと言ってみろ！",
      "time": "00:00:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's close enough.",
      "zh": "這樣差不多了。",
      "ja": "それで十分だ。",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Go!",
      "zh": "走！",
      "ja": "行け！",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Get ready, Malign.",
      "zh": "準備好，惡魔。",
      "ja": "準備しろ、悪者。",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're 17, South Asian.",
      "zh": "你17歲，南亞人。",
      "ja": "君は17歳、南アジア出身だ。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm going to get in.",
      "zh": "我會進去的。",
      "ja": "入隊してみせる。",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I have been sent by your ancestors.",
      "zh": "我是你祖先派來的。",
      "ja": "私は君の先祖に送られた。",
      "time": "00:00:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "To God through your mastery.",
      "zh": "通過你的技藝向神祈禱。",
      "ja": "君の技を通じて神に。",
      "time": "00:00:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Come on, you're going to stay.",
      "zh": "來吧，你會留下的。",
      "ja": "さあ、君はここに残るんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're going to work.",
      "zh": "你會努力的。",
      "ja": "頑張るんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So he's my word.",
      "zh": "這是我的承諾。",
      "ja": "これは私の言葉だ。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Go to the army.",
      "zh": "去軍隊。",
      "ja": "軍隊に行け。",
      "time": "00:00:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Find out your guard.",
      "zh": "找到你的守護。",
      "ja": "守護を見つけろ。",
      "time": "00:00:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The penalty is down.",
      "zh": "懲罰是倒下。",
      "ja": "罰は倒れることだ。",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who are you?",
      "zh": "你是誰？",
      "ja": "あなたは誰？",
      "time": "00:00:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Who am I?",
      "zh": "我是誰？",
      "ja": "私は誰？",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Who am I? Who am I?",
      "zh": "我是誰？我是誰？",
      "ja": "私は誰？私は誰？",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I am the guard in the lost holes.",
      "zh": "我是失落洞穴的守護者。",
      "ja": "私は失われた穴の守護者だ。",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I am the powerful, the plasherner.",
      "zh": "我是強大的，塑造者。",
      "ja": "私は強力な、塑造者だ。",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They're in the structure of the mousse.",
      "zh": "他們在慕斯的結構中。",
      "ja": "彼らはムースの構造の中にいる。",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, I have to do it.",
      "zh": "哦，我得做。",
      "ja": "ああ、やらなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm not.",
      "zh": "我不是。",
      "ja": "私は違う。",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My ancestors sent a little lizard to help me.",
      "zh": "我的祖先派了一隻小蜥蜴來幫我。",
      "ja": "先祖が小さなトカゲを送って助けてくれた。",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, dragon, dragon, not lizard.",
      "zh": "嘿，是龍，不是蜥蜴。",
      "ja": "ねえ、ドラゴンだよ、トカゲじゃない。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I don't do that tongue thing.",
      "zh": "我不會做那種吐舌頭的動作。",
      "ja": "あの舌を出すやつはやらない。",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're intimidating?",
      "zh": "你是在嚇人嗎？",
      "ja": "威嚇してるのか？",
      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "On, Spire?",
      "zh": "在尖塔上？",
      "ja": "尖塔の上？",
      "time": "00:01:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Tiny.",
      "zh": "小小的。",
      "ja": "小さい。",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "もちろん。",
      "time": "00:01:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm travel-sacced for your convenience.",
      "zh": "我縮小了，方便你。",
      "ja": "君のために縮小してるんだ。",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "If I was my real size, you're cow here with that afraid.",
      "zh": "如果我是真正大小，你現在會嚇壞了。",
      "ja": "本当の大きさなら、君は怖がってるだろう。",
      "time": "00:01:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Down, Bessie.",
      "zh": "安靜，貝西。",
      "ja": "おとなしくしろ、ベッシー。",
      "time": "00:01:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "If my power was I'd be on your model of imagination.",
      "zh": "如果我的力量發揮出來，我會超越你的想像。",
      "ja": "もし力を発揮したら、君の想像を超えるだろう。",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "For instance, my eyes can see straight through your armor.",
      "zh": "例如，我的眼睛能穿透你的盔甲。",
      "ja": "例えば、私の目は君の鎧を貫いて見える。",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ow!",
      "zh": "哎呀！",
      "ja": "痛っ！",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All right, that's it.",
      "zh": "好了，就這樣。",
      "ja": "よし、これで終わりだ。",
      "time": "00:01:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This honor.",
      "zh": "這份榮譽。",
      "ja": "この名誉。",
      "time": "00:01:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This honor on your whole family.",
      "zh": "這份榮譽屬於你全家。",
      "ja": "この名誉は君の家族全員のものだ。",
      "time": "00:01:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I can know this.",
      "zh": "我知道這點。",
      "ja": "私はこれを知っている。",
      "time": "00:01:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This honor on you.",
      "zh": "這份榮譽屬於你。",
      "ja": "この名誉は君のものだ。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This honor on your cow.",
      "zh": "這份榮譽屬於你的牛。",
      "ja": "この名誉は君の牛のものだ。",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Stop!",
      "zh": "停下！",
      "ja": "やめろ！",
      "time": "00:01:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "zh": "對不起。",
      "ja": "ごめんなさい。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "zh": "對不起。",
      "ja": "ごめんなさい。",
      "time": "00:01:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm just nervous.",
      "zh": "我只是緊張。",
      "ja": "ただ緊張しているだけだ。",
      "time": "00:01:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I've never done this before.",
      "zh": "我以前從沒做過這事。",
      "ja": "こんなことは初めてだ。",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Then you're going to have to trust me.",
      "zh": "那你得相信我。",
      "ja": "じゃあ、私を信じるしかないな。",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And don't you slap me no more.",
      "zh": "別再打我了。",
      "ja": "もう私を叩かないでくれ。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We clearly aren't there.",
      "zh": "我們顯然還沒到那裡。",
      "ja": "まだそこには達していない。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "よし。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, now get this show in the road.",
      "zh": "好，現在開始行動吧。",
      "ja": "よし、さあ始めよう。",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Tricky, get the bags.",
      "zh": "特里基，拿包包。",
      "ja": "トリッキー、バッグを取れ。",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's move it half up.",
      "zh": "我們快點動身。",
      "ja": "さあ、急ごう。",
      "time": "00:02:10"
    }
  ]
}